name: Smash Trondheim
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
This is Smash Trondheim's website for general info and upcoming events.

Theme and layout is going to change. This is a template theme and layout provided by github.

### Information
Currently Smash Trondheim is running smashfests for Melee, Project M and Brawl at NTNU around 13:30. These smashfests are also streamed at Gardex's twitch channel found at [twitch.tv/gardex](http://www.twitch.tv/gardex)

You can also find us on our facebook group. 

### Upcoming Events
Weekly smashfest at NTNU - Every Saturday at 13:30

TISS5: Turnering i Sverres Sted - March 7th, more info on facebook. 

### Contact
Contact us at smashtrondheim@gmail.com.


### Authors and Contributors
@SmashTrondheim

[SigmaTapion](http://www.github.com/tbTapion)
